data.description: Welcome to your next home! This property is better than new with a full appliance package and window treatments on a large corner lot. This fantastic 3 bed, 2 bath, Hoover MS Ranch Plan by Greenland Homes resale offers space in all the right places. The open floor plan effortlessly flows through an inviting eat-in kitchen with a breakfast bar, quartz countertops, and a stainless-steel appliance package. The exterior stone accents, painted kitchen cabinets, stylish kitchen backsplash, and an electric fireplace with a shiplap surround infuse modern elegance into every corner. With a 2-car garage for added convenience and a large basement ready for future finish, you have plenty of space for everyone. Don't miss your chance to make this remarkable property your own, reach out today to discover living in Altoona!
